title: Catalonia finally gets a new president
text:
Catalonia finally gets a new president 12:14pm EDT - 01:05
Hard-line separatist Quim Torra is sworn in as Catalonia's new leader, bringing an end to seven months of direct rule from Madrid. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
